ing the\nnumber of transitions needed to find the optimal attack transition policy in a\nlarge system such as the Polish 2383 bus test system. The results exhibit how\nthe proposed approach requires one order of magnitude fewer transitions when\ncompared to a random transition policy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Jul 2020 19:16:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 15 Nov 2020 03:05:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-17"}
