y. Furthermore, we\ndemonstrate an enhancement in the volumetric flow rate due to FSI coupling. The\nhydrodynamic pressure oscillations are shown to exhibit a low-pass frequency\nresponse (when averaging over the period of oscillations), while the frequency\nresponse of the tube deformation is similar to that of a band-pass filter.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Jul 2020 21:28:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 1 Oct 2020 17:11:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 22 Jul 2022 20:46:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-26"}
